description: Number of letters in n (in Esperanto).
comments: The links below uses the letter x to indicate an accented letter: 'naux' is actually three letters: n, a, u-breve.
links: Index entries for sequences related to number of letters in n
example: 1 = unu; 2 = du; 3 = tri; 4 = kvar; 5 = kvin; 6 = ses; 7 = sep; 8 = ok; 9 = naux; 10 = dek; ...
